==Notes== The [[Lincancabur]] mountain, located between [[Chile]] and [[Bolivia]], has been rightly referred to be in Argentina under the name ''Lincancaur'' with a height of 6,620 m;this mountain does exist.{{Citation needed|date=March 2010}}
